timeline.bodyText:
(nit) You could probably condense to one statement like:
LOG.error("Refusing to sign attestation:  source epoch ({}) is {}, target epoch ({}) is {}.  Previously signed source epoch {}, target epoch {}", sourceEpoch, sourceEpochIsSafe ? "safe" :  "unsafe", targetEpoch, targetEpochIsSafe ? "safe" :  "unsafe", attestationSourceEpoch, attestationTargetEpoch);

I'd also use string interpolation ({}) instead of concatenating.

